item.title: Fall 2019 Classes
Shuttle
item.description: Hello Engineering Students, Faculty, and Staff! As the semester approaches, I wanted to remind everyone that there is a shuttle to transport ISE students and personnel between Luddy Hall and MESH during the academic year when class is in session. Shuttle Service between Luddy Hall & MESH is available Monday – Friday from 8AM – 5PM from IU Fleet Services DSS Van Service. Call 812-855-5043 at least 10 minutes before a ride is needed to request a ride.
